        <article
                class="program-show"
                data-episode-id="821886935" data-episode-date="2020-03-27">

                <div class="program-show__info">
                    <div class="program-show__info-inner">
                        <h2 class="program-show__title">
                            <a href="https://www.npr.org/programs/ted-radio-hour/821886935/uncharted?showDate=2020-03-27"  data-metrics='{"action":"Click Archive View Full Show","category":"Episode Archive","label":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/programs\/ted-radio-hour\/821886935\/uncharted"}' >Uncharted</a>
                        </h2>

                            <p class="program-show__teaser"><time datetime="2020-03-27"><span class="date">March 27, 2020 &#149; </span></time>There's so much we've yet to explorefrom outer space to the deep ocean to our own brains. This hour, Manoush goes on a journey through those uncharted places, led by TED Science Curator David Biello.</p>

                            <div class="program-show__full-audio">
                                  <b data-play-all='{"type":"episode","full":["821886935:822013901"],"segments":["821887731:822016232"],"audioData":[{"uid":"821886935:822013901","available":true,"duration":"3149","title":"Uncharted","audioUrl":"https:\/\/ondemand.npr.org\/anon.npr-mp3\/npr\/ted\/2020\/03\/20200327_ted_ep_159_full.mp3?d=3149&story=821886935&t=fullprog&p=&siteplayer=true&size=46696494","storyUrl":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/programs\/ted-radio-hour\/821886935\/uncharted","slug":"","program":"TED Radio Hour","affiliation":null,"song":"","artist":"","album":"","track":"","type":"segment","subtype":"program"},{"uid":"821887731:822016232","available":true,"duration":3149,"title":"David Biello: A Journey Into Uncharted Territory","audioUrl":"https:\/\/ondemand.npr.org\/anon.npr-mp3\/npr\/ted\/2020\/03\/20200327_ted_ep_159_full.mp3?orgId=1&topicId=1008&d=3149&p=57&story=821887731&siteplayer=true&size=46696494","storyUrl":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/2020\/03\/27\/821887731\/david-biello-a-journey-into-uncharted-territory","slug":"Arts & Life","program":"TED Radio Hour","affiliation":"","song":"","artist":"","album":"","track":0,"type":"segment","subtype":"other"}]}'></b>


